    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In our life, a new day comes every day&lt;br&gt;
but only once in 365 days a new day also comes with the new year.&lt;br&gt;
Like the circle of 360 degrees, 365 days of a year also represents a circle of time.&lt;br&gt;
Only a few who learn from the previous circle and&lt;br&gt;
plan for a new circle move vertically in the circle&lt;br&gt;
and create a spring of evolution in life.&lt;br&gt;
For others, it is like moving around the same circle throughout life,&lt;br&gt;
like in the picture above.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
